import React from 'react';
import { Container, Segment, Grid, Button, Form, Divider } from 'semantic-ui-react'

function App() {
  return (
    <Container style={{ margin: 20 }}>
      <Segment>
        <Grid columns={2} relaxed="very" stackable>
          <Grid.Row>
          <Grid.Column>
            <Form>
              <Form.Input
                icon='search'
                iconPosition='left'
                label='Search'
                placeholder='Search'
              />
            </Form>
          </Grid.Column>
          <Grid.Column verticalAlign='middle'>
            <Button content="Search" primary />
            <Button content="Notes" primary />
          </Grid.Column>
          </Grid.Row>
        </Grid>
        
      </Segment>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default App;
